===============
 Base Accounts
===============

Synopsis:

Manage account configuration. Accounts represent connectivity to external systems. Includes support for:

• Email (POP/IMAP/SMTP)
• Calendars (CalDAV)
• Contacts (CardDAV)
• XMPP

Usage:

Account manager associated with registered repository instance will be provided as a service for performing account CRUD operations.

Services:

• Account Manager (CRUD/enable/disable)

Dependencies:

• base-repository (store account configurations)

